&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own radiometric and geometric calibration standards across multiple instrument programs, developing best practices and ensuring adherence to defined processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the design and development of scalable calibration test hardware infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the planning and execution of pre-launch radiometric and geometric calibration campaigns to establish baseline sensor performance models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support definition and tracking of metrics to monitor the performance of instruments from ground to orbit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate and communicate effectively with instrument and spacecraft systems engineers, data scientists, mission operations engineers, and program managers.&lt;/li&gt;
