&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PhD with 3+ years of industry experience; or MS with 6+ years industry experience; or BS +8 years industry experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience building geospatial data products from remote sensing data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with image mosaicking, orthorectification, or related geospatial image processing techniques&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with real-world data from new or novel imaging instruments&lt;/li&gt;
